trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameElement class represents a configuration element for a service name used in a <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ServiceNameElement representerer en konfigurasjonselementet for en tjeneste som brukes i en <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When this constructor is used to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> class, the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Når denne konstruktøren brukes til å initialisere en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>klassen den <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>er satt til `null`.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property should be set to an appropriate value for the application before calling the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> method to add the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> instance to the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>Egenskapen må være satt til riktig verdi for programmet før du kaller <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>metode for å legge til <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>forekomsten til <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>klasse.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Service Provider Name (SPN) for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir leverandøren navnet SPN (Service) for denne <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the representation of SPN for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder representasjon av SPN for denne <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> forekomsten.</xref:System.String>
